@startuml ui_navigation
!theme plain
title Air Quality Node – UI Flow & Menu Navigation

skinparam state {
  BackgroundColor<<menu>> #C8E6C9
  BackgroundColor<<screen>> #BBDEFB
  BackgroundColor<<dashboard>> #E1BEE7
}

state "Dashboard View" as DASH <<dashboard>> {
  state "AQI Circle + Sensor Bars\n+ WiFi Icon + Time + Date" as DASH_VIEW
}

state "Local Menu (5 items)" as MENU <<menu>> {
  state "Monitor" as M0 <<menu>>
  state "WiFi" as M1 <<menu>>
  state "Alarm" as M2 <<menu>>
  state "Game" as M3 <<menu>>
  state "Memory" as M4 <<menu>>

  M0 -[hidden]down-> M1
  M1 -[hidden]down-> M2
  M2 -[hidden]down-> M3
  M3 -[hidden]down-> M4
}

state "WiFi Panel" as SWIFI <<screen>> : SSID, IP, Status\nProvisioning info

state "Memory Panel" as SMEM <<screen>> : Photo display\nRGB565 160×128

state "Alarm Panel" as SALARM <<screen>> : Alarm settings

state "Game Panel" as SGAME <<screen>> : Mini game

[*] --> DASH : Boot complete\n(RUNNING phase)

' ── Dashboard ↔ Menu ──
DASH --> MENU : UI_FLOW_EVENT_SET_SCREEN\n(menu activated)
MENU --> DASH : Select "Monitor"\nor autoplay ends

' ── Menu → Screen panels ──
M1 --> SWIFI : Select "WiFi"\n→ MENU_SMOKE_PHASE_SCREEN_WIFI
M4 --> SMEM  : Select "Memory"\n→ MENU_SMOKE_PHASE_SCREEN_MEMORY

' ── Return from screens ──
SWIFI --> M1 : Return\n→ MENU_SMOKE_PHASE_MENU_RETURN_WIFI
SMEM  --> M0 : Return\n→ MENU_SMOKE_PHASE_RETURN_MONITOR

' ── External events ──
DASH --> SMEM : UI_FLOW_EVENT_MEMORY_PHOTO_UPDATED\n(photo uploaded via HTTP)
SMEM --> DASH : UI_FLOW_EVENT_MEMORY_PHOTO_CLEARED\n(photo deleted via HTTP)

note bottom of MENU
  **Autoplay Demo (AQI ≥ 5)**
  Cycle: Monitor → WiFi → WiFi Screen (5s)
  → WiFi → Alarm → Game → Memory
  → Memory Screen (5s) → Monitor
  Each menu item: 1400ms
  Return: 1800ms
end note

note right of MENU
  **Highlight Animation**
  Q8 fixed-point physics
  Y targets: [36, 54, 72, 90, 108]
  Spacing: 18px per item
  Accel: diff/3 (clamped ±1)
  Velocity damping: ×27/32
  Velocity clamp: ±520
end note

@enduml
